Key Features Implemented:
PNG Image Integration: Uses your three images (sharingan.png, ems.png, rinnegan.png) throughout the UI for:
Logo/brand identity in sidebar
Theme selection previews
Power level indicators
Premium feature badges
License status display
Visual Theme System:
Tomoe (Sharingan): Free tier, basic rotation animation
Eternal Mangekyo (EMS): Premium tier, continuous rotation glow
Rinnegan: Developer tier, locked by default with pulsing animation
Interactive Elements:
Real-time settings sync with Chrome storage
Custom hotkey recording system
Dynamic power level indicators
Toast notifications
Smooth page transitions
Responsive Layout: Sidebar navigation with card-based settings grid
Security/Privacy: Privacy mode toggle, cache management, data retention controls
Place these files in ui/options/ and ensure your PNG images are in build/assets/icons/. The paths are relative from the options page location.